HEADWORD: Jump
<hw>Jump</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Nice; exact; matched; fitting;
precise.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Jump</xex> names.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jump</ent>⟦br⟧

