HEADWORD: Jump
<hw>Jump</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Exactly; pat.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>jump</ent>⟦br⟧

